*** Step 1: Install dependencies ***

* Install Maven.  These examples have been verified to work with Maven 2.0.11 
and 3.0.3.  Other versions may work but have not been tested.
http://maven.apache.org/download.html

* Install Git
http://git-scm.com/download


*** Step 2: Check out example code ***
git clone git://github.com/jbaldassari/Avro-RPC


*** Step 3: Build/run example code ***
cd Avro-RPC
mvn test

